er’ position.</span></p><p>https://seekingalpha.com/instablog/498952-bret-jensen/5074614-epizyme-upcoming-catalysts-horizon?app=1&amp;uprof=45&amp;isDirectRoadblock=true</p>', 15, 'BUSTED IPO EMAIL', 3, '2017-11-20 16:00:00', 1, 0, 0, '0.00', null, 12.85, 6, '2017-11-21 14:29:55', '2017-11-21 14:29:55');
